data.description: 123 Woodshire Drive is a beautiful home in excellent condition located just a short walk or drive to the beach. This is one of the most competitively priced homes located SOUTH of HWY 98. The bike path at the entrance to the community takes you all the way to 30A where you can head to the beach or walk/bike to all the restaurants and shopping at Gulf Place. 10 foot ceilings welcome you into the open living room. The living and dining flow into the custom kitchen creating one continuous entertaining room. The second level features the master bedroom suite plus two additional bedrooms, additional bathroom and washroom. The master bath features dual vanities, glassed in shower, soaker tub and walk in closet. This is a low maintenance well-built home that is move in ready today.
